State.Name: Apocalypse - Magic of Skyrim
State.Author: Enai Siaion
State.Description: Apocalypse is the most popular Skyrim spell pack, adding 155 new spells that are unique, balanced, lore friendly, use high quality custom visuals and blend seamlessly into the vanilla magic system. Also includes scrolls and staves for the new spells.

Archives.Name: Apocalypse - Ordinator Compatibility Patch WHY DO I HAVE TO CHANGE THE NAME-1090-.zip

State.Name: Apocalypse - Magic of Skyrim
State.Author: Enai Siaion
State.Description: Apocalypse is the most popular Skyrim spell pack, adding 155 new spells that are unique, balanced, lore friendly, use high quality custom visuals and blend seamlessly into the vanilla magic system. Also includes scrolls and staves for the new spells.

State.Name: Arcanum - A New Age of Magic
State.Author: Kosorsomesaykosm
State.Description: Years in the making, Arcanum is a massive spell mod that aims to combine unique gameplay with visual effects of a quality never attempted before in Skyrim. With 200 spells complete, 300+ spells planned, and inspired by everything from Dragon's Dogma to Planescape, Arcanum may be the most ambitious magic mod ever made.

State.Name: Buff Others for Skyrim Together SSE
State.Author: Jinxxed0
State.Description: Adds spells that allow you to buff other players and NPCs with things like magic resistance, water walking, and other stuff.

State.Name: Growl - Werebeasts of Skyrim
State.Author: Enai Siaion
State.Description: Growl is a lightweight werewolf and werebear overhaul. Better werebeast combat, scaling, experience gain, reworked perks, synergies between beast and mortal form, lunar transformations, werebears and many quality of life improvements. Growl makes werebeasts a viable choice without "taking over" or imbalancing the game.

State.Name: MCM Helper
State.Author: Parapets
State.Description: Simplifies the creation of Mod Configuration Menus and extends them with powerful new features, such as persistent INI settings and hotkey registration. Mod authors will be able to write simpler, cleaner Papyrus scripts for their configs. Players will be able to spend less time in menus.

State.Name: Mealtime - A simple ESO inspired Food Overhaul
State.Author: SaiMika
State.Description: Immerse yourself with meals that now provide prolonged benefits, separate to alchemy effects. A full adventurer is a happy adventurer.

State.Name: NordWarUA's Vanilla Armor Replacers SSE
State.Author: NordWarUA
State.Description: This mod retextures some of the armor sets and weapon sets from the base game to a more High Medieval aesthetic. It also adds a new armor set that looks similar to the one from the Skyrim trailer.

Archives.Name: Open Wayshrines for SWIFT - tidy - Skyrim Wayshrines Immersive Fast Travel-30372-1-0-0-1573794480.rar

State.Name: Open Wayshrines Add-on for SWIFT -  Skyrim Wayshrines Immersive Fast Travel
State.Author: SaiMika
State.Description: Opens up the walls of the snow elf wayshrines, and (optionally) tidies up the shrines themselves. A huge thank you to LeanWolf for the amazing open wayshrine model.

State.Name: Ordinator - Perks of Skyrim
State.Author: Enai Siaion
State.Description: Ordinator overhauls the perk trees of Skyrim to increase the depth and fun of character building. It is highly compatible with other mods and uses lightweight and clean scripting.

State.Name: Redux SE
State.Author: Craftian
State.Description: A unique, fully-voiced overhaul of the main quest, adding a campaign designed to play to Skyrim's strengths as an open world sandbox.

State.Name: Sacrosanct - Vampires of Skyrim
State.Author: Enai Siaion
State.Description: Sacrosanct overhauls vampires and vampire lords. Reverse progression (stronger when fed), new abilities, powers, perks, hemomancy, various new progression systems and many gameplay tweaks for the discerning undead monster.

State.Name: SkyrimTogether Plus
State.Author: PoPoWanObi
State.Description: ST+ or Skyrim Together Plus is an expansion mod designed for the sole purpose of being used in synergy with Skyrim Together. It provides game-play improving additions and changes to make the multiplayer experience better.

State.Name: Skyrim Wayshrines - Immersive Fast Travel - SWIFT SE
State.Author: Pharros
State.Description: A brand new fast travel network created with lore-friendliness and immersion in mind. Best of all it features ZERO time transition, which is most suitable for any weather and needs survivalist out there.

State.Name: Skyshards
State.Author: Deadmano
State.Description:
Skyshards brings the joy of Skyshard hunting based on the MMO "The Elder Scrolls Online" (ESO) to Skyrim!

Every 3 (default) Skyshards absorbed rewards you with a perk point to invest as you please.

State.Name: SkyUI
State.Author: SkyUI Team
State.Description: Elegant, PC-friendly interface mod with many advanced features.

State.Name: Smooth Random Jump Animation
State.Author: Smooth
State.Description: Random Jump Animation

State.Name: TK Dodge SE
State.Author: tktk
State.Description: This mod adds dodge animation of using key press when player drawn weapons,spell,staff and unarmed.

State.Name: True Directional Movement - Modernized Third Person Gameplay
State.Author: Ersh
State.Description: Overhauls the third person gameplay similarly to modern action RPGs, entirely through SKSE. Move and attack in any direction. Includes a custom target lock component and animated healthbar widget, target headtracking, projectile aim support during target lock, boss bars, mount support and more! Modular and customizable through MCM.

State.Name: TrueHUD - HUD Additions
State.Author: Ersh
State.Description: HUD additions formerly included in True Directional Movement, completely reworked and improved! Very customizable actor info bars, boss bars, player widget and an API for other plugins to use. Modular and customizable through MCM.

State.Name: UIExtensions
State.Author: Expired
State.Description: Adds various custom menus to Skyrim for modder use.

State.Name: Unofficial Skyrim Special Edition Patch
State.Author: Unofficial Patch Project Team
State.Description: A comprehensive bugfixing mod for The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim - Special Edition. The goal of the Unofficial Skyrim Special Edition Patch (aka USSEP) is to eventually fix every bug with Skyrim Special Edition not officially resolved by the developers to the limits of the Creation Kit and community-developed tools, in one easy-to-install package.

Archives.Name: Weapons Armor Clothing and Clutter Fixes-18994-2-8-1638839265.7z

State.Name: Weapons Armor Clothing and Clutter Fixes
State.Author: kryptopyr
State.Description: Fixes bugs and inconsistencies for Skyrim's weapons, armors, clothing, jewelry, and clutter items.

State.Name: Wildcat - Combat of Skyrim
State.Author: Enai Siaion
State.Description: Wildcat is a streamlined, yet full featured combat overhaul. It makes combat more dangerous and visceral by increasing lethality, adding injuries and context sensitive stagger and making combat AI more responsive and aggressive. It accomplishes this with minimal scripting and no save bloat.

State.Name: XP32 Maximum Skeleton Special Extended - XPMSSE
State.Author: Team XPMSE
State.Description: XP32 Maximum Skeleton Special  Extended is the update of XP32 Maximum Skeleton Extended for Skyrim Special Edition.

State.Name: QUI (Alpha)
State.Author: Qudix
State.Description: Various UI tools, tweaks, and fixes. More than functional, but not fully "complete". Includes an AddItemMenu alternative.

State.Name: Remove QuickSave Button from SkyUI System Menu
State.Author: uranreactor
State.Description:
This small mod removes the "Quick Save" button from System Menu (esc), that was added in SE.

You can now normally exit your game without scrolling in System Menu.

State.Name: Skyrim Together Reborn
State.Author: The Together Team
State.Description: Play Skyrim in co-op with your friends or strangers, complete quests, fight, explore the world.

State.Name: Address Library for SKSE Plugins
State.Author: meh321
State.Description: Contains header file and a database to make SKSE DLL plugins version independent easily.

State.Name: Animation Motion Revolution
State.Author: alexsylex
State.Description: This SKSE plugin removes the mismatch between displacement and custom animations driven by motion data (the infamous ice-skating problem). Welcome to 2021 guys.

State.Name: Better Jumping SE
State.Author: meh321 and z65536
State.Description: Allows to jump while sprinting. Also you can configure jump height multiplier, how many times you can jump (double jump like in action games) . No ESP!

State.Name: Disable Fast Travel SKSE - No Janky Map UI
State.Author: Parapets
State.Description: Disables fast travel in the map menu, and fixes the bug where you would no longer be able to place custom markers near discovered locations.

State.Name: Dynamic Animation Replacer
State.Author: Felisky
State.Description: This mod dynamically replaces the actors' animations depending on various conditions. Supports most actors, including creatures. Actors and animations added by mods are also supported. No ESP file.

State.Name: VR Address Library for SKSEVR
State.Author: alandtse
State.Description:
VR Address Library database for end users. This is intended as a VR replacement for Address Library for SKSE for mods designed for it. Only download if the mod says this is a requirement. It is currently an alpha.



This is not for SSE. This is different from Address Library for SKSE.

State.Name: Proper Console Disabler
State.Author: Fairace
State.Description: Proper Console Disabler - For people who has the itch to press ~. Simple mod, NO SCRIPTS, Save game compatible, Enable/Disable anytime via your mod loader.

Archives.Name: No Wait Function and No Console Command-71445-0-0-1-1657902899.zip

State.Name: No Wait Function and No Console Button - For Skyrim Together Reborn
State.Author: Mailoko
State.Description: Remove shortcut key for commands admin and wait time

State.Name: Goetia Animations - Enchanted Staves
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: Hand made animations that completely overhaul Skyrim's 3rd person enchanted staff playstyles, designed to work with hybrid playstyles as well (staff+melee or staff+spell), requires DAR.

State.Name: Goetia Animations - Magic Spell Casting
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: At 110 animation files made from scratch (v1.0), I'm glad to finally bring you this 3rd person spell casting animation overhaul, works for all spell categories and for spellsword/hybrid playstyles, requires DAR.

Archives.Name: Leviathan Animations - Two-Handed High Stance SE-47092-1-4-1622760836.7z

State.Name: Leviathan Animations - Two-Handed High Stance
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: Replaces vanilla unsheathe, idle, block, turn, walk, run, sprint and sheathe animations for two-handed weapons (swords, hammers and axes) with a high stance variant.

Archives.Name: Leviathan Animations - Two-Handed Normal Attacks For High Stance-48550-1-2-1622761129.7z

State.Name: Leviathan Animations - Two-Handed Normal Attacks
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: Replaces vanilla normal attack animations for two-handed weapons (swords, hammers and axes).

Archives.Name: Leviathan Animations - Two-Handed Power Attacks For High Stance-50545-1-3-1622761240.7z

State.Name: Leviathan Animations - Two-Handed Power Attacks
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: Replaces vanilla power attack animations for two-handed weapons (swords, hammers and axes).

State.Name: Vanargand Animations - Archery
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: Without requirements, these animations will completely replace, while holding a bow, the Idle, walk, run, turn left/right, Sprint, draw arrow, drawn arrow idle, drawn arrow walk/turn, arrow release, equip and unequip, includes belt fasted quiver animations.

State.Name: Vanargand Animations - Dual Wield Attacks
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: I'm glad to finally bring you this vanilla replacer dual wield combat set, this was quite fun and really challenging to make and has at last reached a quality state I'm happy with.

Archives.Name: Vanargand Animations - One handed Mid Stance-57544-1-2-1637000570.7z

State.Name: Vanargand Animations - One Handed Mid Stance
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: These animations will replace, While holding a one-handed weapon in the right hand, the idle, walk, run, strafe, sprint, turn left/right and sword equip/unequip, including dual wielding.

Archives.Name: Vanargand Animations - One handed Normal Attacks-58326-1-1-1636745710.7z

State.Name: Vanargand Animations - One Handed Normal Attacks
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: These animations will replace vanilla normal attack animations for one-handed weapons while standing still or moving in any direction. No requirements.

Archives.Name: Vanargand Animations - One Handed Power Attacks-58997-1-2-1637780789.7z

State.Name: Vanargand Animations - One Handed Power Attacks
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: Replaces vanilla power attack animations for one-handed weapons while standing still or while moving in any direction. Using Animation Motion Revolution for custom motion data.

Archives.Name: Goetia Animations - Female Idle Walk And Run-68005-1-2-1656538843.7z

State.Name: Goetia Animations - Female Idle Walk And Run
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: Animation pack for female characters. no requirement replacer version and DAR version.

State.Name: Goetia Animations - Male Idle Walk And Run
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: Goetia Animation pack for male characters, no requirement replacer version and DAR version.

State.Name: Goetia Animations - Sprint
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: Sprint animations for male and female characters (PC and NPCs), DAR version and simple no requirement replacer version.

State.Name: Vanargand Animations - Crossbows
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: Replaces crossbow animations and fixes jittery crossbow aim direction while moving and/or turning.

State.Name: Vanargand Animations - Dual Wield Sneak Strikes
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: Replaces sneak attacks and movement animations while Dual Wielding (Left hand, right hand and dual hand normal and power attacks) and holding an axe/mace, using DAR and AMR.

Archives.Name: Vanargand Animations - Dual Wield Sneak Thrusts-64577-1-0-1646513184.7z

State.Name: Vanargand Animations - Dual Wield Sneak Thrusts
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: Replaces sneak attacks and movement animations while Dual Wielding (Left hand, right hand and dual hand normal and power attacks) and holding a Sword/Dagger, using DAR and AMR.

State.Name: Vanargand Animations - Sneak Archery
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: A new animation pack, using DAR, aimed at bringing a more modern experience into the Sneak Archery archetype and eliminating long standing issues with the vanilla animations (bow changing direction while aiming, jittery movement and bow handling).

State.Name: Vanargand Animations - Sneak Crossbows
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: The sneak counterpart of Vanargand Crossbows, replaces sneak crossbow animations and fixes jittery crossbow aim direction while moving and/or turning.

State.Name: Vanargand Animations - Sneak idle walk and run
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: Animations for the sneak idle, sneak walk and sneak run, while no weapon is drawn, using DAR.

State.Name: Vanargand Animations - Sneak Strike Attacks
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: The third part of the Vanargand Sneak animations, revamping animations for axes and hammers while sneaking. Standard version and SkySA adapted version.

State.Name: Vanargand Animations - Sneak Thrust Attacks
State.Author: Verolevi
State.Description: The second part of the Vanargand Sneak animations, revamping animations for swords and daggers while sneaking. Standard version and SkySA version.
